{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1738254120\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1738254120\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Doomed Hell 64 is a retro FPS where you battle through hellish levels filled with monsters and chaos. Battle through endless waves, discover the hidden secrets of hell, and obliterate all living forms!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/BT_Text_Steam_BLAST_EN_red.png?t=1738254120\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/9d1614c56b350884580ad88b9b9586d8.gif?t=1738254120\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Doomed Hell 64</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Doomed Hell 64 is a retro old school FPS dungeon crawler that throws you into the depths of a chaotic, monster-infested hell. Fight your way through intense levels in campaign mode, face off against endless waves of enemies, and challenge yourself in various modes, including Arcade and Deadly Race. With procedurally generated scenarios, fast-paced combat, and a wide selection of powerful weapons, every battle feels fresh and full of adrenaline!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/BT_Text_Steam_MAIM_EN_red.png?t=1738254120\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/02eab5e9b589e05c7b690861939885bd.gif?t=1738254120\" /></p><h